OL,3,CHow can I get a refund or compensation
OL,4,Cfor train delays?
OL,6,FTrain services across the UK have
OL,7,Ffaced cancellations and delays as a
OL,8,Fresult of the severe weather this
OL,9,Fweekend.
OL,11,FDisrupted passengers may be entitled
OL,12,Fto a full refund from the ticket
OL,13,Fretailer or compensation from the
OL,14,Ftrain company responsible for the
OL,15,Fdelay.
OL,17,FBut how can you claim a refund or
OL,18,Fcompensation? ITV News explains.
