OL,3,CHow can I get a refund or compensation
OL,4,Cfor train delays?
OL,6,FYes, if your train is delayed or
OL,7,Fcancelled and you decide not to
OL,8,Ftravel, you can get a full refund for
OL,9,Fyour unused ticket at no extra cost.
OL,11,FIf you want to get a refund for
OL,12,Fanother reason, you may have to pay a
OL,13,Ffee.
OL,15,FContact the retailer where you bought
OL,16,Fthe ticket for a refund.
OL,18,FIf it was purchased directly from a
OL,19,Ftrain company, reach out to them for
OL,20,Fassistance. You can find their contact
OL,21,Finformation here.
