OL,3,CHow can I get a refund or compensation
OL,4,Cfor train delays?
OL,6,FFor tickets bought from self-service
OL,7,Fmachines, check the machine or station
OL,8,Ffor refund instructions.
OL,10,FAm I entitled to compensation, and how
OL,11,Fdo I claim it?
OL,13,FIf your train is delayed or cancelled
OL,14,Fand you arrive late at your
OL,15,Fdestination, you may be entitled to
OL,16,Fcompensation.
OL,18,FTo claim, you must contact the train
OL,19,Fcompany you travelled with, as
OL,20,Fcompensation schemes vary by operator.
