OL,3,CHow can I get a refund or compensation
OL,4,Cfor train delays?
OL,6,FYou can claim if your journey is
OL,7,Fdelayed for any reason. The delay is
OL,8,Fmeasured against the regular timetable
OL,9,For an amended one published in
OL,10,Fadvance, such as during planned
OL,11,Fengineering works.
OL,13,FCheck your train company's website for
OL,14,Fdetails of their compensation policy
OL,15,Fand how to submit a claim.
